Procedure InitialiseSystem:
    Set initial power mode to highest Power Mode for both components

Procedure CheckRocketStatus:
    Return Altimeter reading to determine if landed (altitude near zero or if there is no changes to height after a certain period of time)

Procedure SwitchToLowPowerMode:
    If CheckRocketStatus indicates landing:
        Set all Components to LOWEST power mode

Procedure Main:
    InitialiseSystem()
    Loop:
        If CheckRocketStatus indicates landing:
            SwitchToLowPowerMode()
        Delay for a set interval (check every 10 seconds)
